{"name":"Accurate Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an accurate attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on the effect modifier of the attack and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"0duspgdqv3w"}
{"name":"Agile Feint","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use your Acrobatics bonus or movement speed rank in place of Deception to feint and trick in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"pj32ievuqq"}
{"name":"All-out Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an all-out attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on your active defenses (Dodge and Parry) and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"of4u9ygundm"}
{"name":"Animal Empathy","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have a special connection with animals. You can use interaction skills on animals normally, and do not have to speak a language the animal understands.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"19pwn5ghvo9"}
{"name":"Artificer","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use the Expertise: Magic skill to create temporary magical devices.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"l6981tsghyq"}
{"name":"Assessment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use Insight to able to judge an opponent’s relative combat capabilities.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"6rc4mnye83f"}
{"name":"Attractive","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You are particularly attractive, giving you a +2 circumstance bonus on Deception and Persuasion checks to deceive, mislead, or influence others who are attracted to you. Rank 2 gives a +5 bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"i184me5n5r"}
{"name":"Beginner's Luck","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>By spending a hero point, you gain an effective 5 ranks in a skill in which you currently have 0 ranks.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"0spq44p6jq4"}
{"name":"Benefit","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have some significant social or structural benefit, such as wealth, status, or a secret identity. Each rank provides one benefit.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"5htmhngm2xg"}
{"name":"Chokehold","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you successfully grab and maintain a hold on an opponent, you can suffocate them.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"7nlxhcogjdj"}
{"name":"Connected","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You know people who can help you out. You can call in favors by making a Persuasion check.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"qqlmeb9wkp8"}
{"name":"Contacts","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have extensive contacts. You can make an Investigation check to gather information in only one minute.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"lhs89woaefj"}
{"name":"Daze","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can make a Deception or Intimidation check as a standard action to cause an opponent to hesitate in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":2,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"fev3pw9mt2"}
{"name":"Defensive Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Trade up to -5 attack bonus for an equal bonus (+5) to active defenses.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"bxbgh0wh3yl"}
{"name":"Defensive Roll","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Receive a bonus to Toughness equal to rank. This is an active defense and is lost if vulnerable or defenseless.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"isox35ul2xa"}
{"name":"Diehard","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Automatically stabilize on the round after your condition becomes dying.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"d97aup5dr1b"}
{"name":"Eidetic Memory","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Perfect recall. +5 circumstance bonus on memory checks. Can make Expertise checks as if trained.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"0myi4t18jb8"}
